Text: I have a newbie problem: I've been seeding for some hours now, the torrent app says that the file has been served several times, but it doesn't show in this page. What did I do wrong? How can I fix it?

You did nothing wrong except seeding this awesome masterpiece too much for a lot of fucking ungrateful leechers on this place ;) It seems deleting the tracker announce from the torrent is in fashion these days. That means statistics are not accurate anymore since seeders/leechers are not reported back to tracker. I've seen torrents with thousands of peers and 0/0 stats. No need to worry.

Btw, an amazing album, although I already had it ;)
Thank you for continuing to seed this album! Was SO hard to find it. I am very pleased!
